<b><a name="faq1">What is mindfulness?</a></b>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<a href="#top">Back to Top</a>


<p> 
Mindfulness is often defined as paying attention to the present moment with an attitude of equanimity that is
friendly and accepting rather than being critical.
</p>
